snippet.title: Snout Clout [Gameplay]
snippet.description:
Download for Windows or macOS: 
https://sikeology.itch.io/snout-clout

Snout Clout is a game project my friend stekra and I worked on. It's a local multiplayer couch potato game in which you joust with your friends. The prototype is finished for now and might get updates if we have time to work on it.
